Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.26,0:01:52.66,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰かを悲しませてまで　笑えなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.81,0:02:03.41,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そう言って彼女はうつむいてたんだ　夜に泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.14,0:02:11.00,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷たく貼り付いて　凍えている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.20,0:02:17.96,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降り続く現実に　傘などない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.54,0:02:24.70,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生きてゆくことが　戦いなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.81,0:02:28.43,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そんな理由だけで　閉じ込められた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.53,0:02:31.32,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My Heart　My Story
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.48,0:02:38.81,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泪のムコウが見えるの　輝いている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.02,0:02:45.51,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小さな窓には　あの頃みたいに　青い空が映る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.78,0:02:52.26,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ah  ah　鳥のように　飛べはしないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:03:03.74,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰かを悲しませたとき　感じる痛み
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:05.52,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘れないように
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.64,0:03:11.10,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そっと目を閉じて　泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.26,0:01:52.66,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在傷害別人之前　不必強顏歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.81,0:02:03.41,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說著她低下頭　在黑夜裡哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.14,0:02:11.00,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰冷黏合在一起　渾身僵硬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.20,0:02:17.96,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨下個不停　卻沒有傘來遮擋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.54,0:02:24.70,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己囚禁在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.81,0:02:28.43,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有戰鬥才能求生的因果之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.53,0:02:31.32,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心　我的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.48,0:02:38.81,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淚水的彼岸所見到的　是五彩光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.02,0:02:45.51,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小的窗口　映照出那時蔚藍的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.78,0:02:52.26,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　雖說不能像鳥兒一樣自由翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:03:03.74,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷害別人之後的那份心痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:05.52,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不忘卻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.64,0:03:11.10,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕輕地閉上眼　哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.15,0:03:25.66,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}#19  改革者之影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.46,0:00:11.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞斯  快逃！保安局的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.26,0:00:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱利！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.11,0:00:17.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危險  大家到這來！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.21,0:00:18.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們帶上孩子們快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.04,0:00:23.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！約瑟夫！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.41,0:00:27.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.06,0:00:36.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.91,0:00:37.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.70,0:00:39.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.25,0:00:41.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.19,0:00:51.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死的聯邦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.41,0:00:55.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.32,0:00:59.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.87,0:01:01.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.81,0:01:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20世紀戰爭時期建造的防空洞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.31,0:01:09.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裡穿過去就能到後山去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.10,0:01:11.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞斯呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.06,0:01:14.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就只考慮怎麼逃出這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.55,0:01:23.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.76,0:01:33.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊  都已經是這種情況了還猶豫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.98,0:01:41.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我拿了槍的話  就再也無法正視這些孩子的眼睛了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.32,0:03:28.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員準備以戰術計劃S43迎擊敵MS部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.00,0:03:32.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵機有12台  大概還會有增援
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.72,0:03:34.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家別掉以輕心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.08,0:03:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:36.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:37.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:39.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.17,0:03:42.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈  去見路易絲·哈萊維吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:43.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.79,0:03:45.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.89,0:03:49.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OO Raiser  先行出擊攻擊敵部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.92,0:04:06.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出她的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:07.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.34,0:04:12.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別以為是Twin Drive就…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.14,0:04:20.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到改革者的機體了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.00,0:04:21.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特瑞亞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.31,0:04:23.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:26.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:31.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:36.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲的機體呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.99,0:04:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左右兩側有敵MS增援
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:46.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.31,0:04:47.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總數14台
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.66,0:04:50.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓Arios和Cherudim執行至計劃D67
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:52.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞琉  進行回避運動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.22,0:05:00.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用導彈張開彈幕  瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.68,0:05:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是蘇摩·佩麗絲！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.32,0:05:14.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.80,0:05:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.82,0:05:19.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:27.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪裡？安德烈少尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別太衝到前面去  瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:43.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵機接近  敵機接近
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.39,0:05:47.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅  Shield Bit強擊模式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.31,0:05:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白  明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:06:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你們打掉的話  不管亞琉是哪裡的什麼人…！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:05.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OO已經出擊了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.92,0:06:11.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  就交給你了  希琳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:19.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據吠陀的預測他的細胞異常應該是致死級別的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.31,0:06:24.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與Twin Drive有關？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:30.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…變革已經開始了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:32.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那·F·清榮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:36.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈  她的機體呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.16,0:06:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.51,0:06:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細找找
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.56,0:06:40.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經在做了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.64,0:06:46.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.43,0:06:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.87,0:06:52.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來送你們兩個回家吧  連布林格和迪拜因的份也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.19,0:06:57.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  有兩個接近母艦的隕石
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.84,0:06:58.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.09,0:07:01.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥中居然東張西望…！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:05.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧  在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.06,0:07:07.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:08.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦量子波？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.27,0:07:21.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找路易絲？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.82,0:07:23.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.84,0:07:25.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種加速粒子…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.31,0:07:28.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們的腦量子波興奮不已！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.23,0:07:36.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧…阿里路亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.51,0:07:42.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有MS從隕石裡出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.72,0:07:44.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會再中這招了  拉塞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.26,0:07:47.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白  導彈一起發射
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.13,0:07:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.22,0:07:51.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:52.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.89,0:07:53.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.87,0:07:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:59.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那光芒…又是幻聽嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.03,0:08:06.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在等你  想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.52,0:08:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是兵器  不是破壞者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.92,0:08:15.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和Gundam在改變！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:17.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.96,0:08:21.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.18,0:08:28.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲  路易絲！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙…沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.87,0:08:34.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  是我  沙慈·克洛斯羅德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:36.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個光芒是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.02,0:08:50.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子釋放量是通常的7倍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.74,0:08:53.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是Twin Drive的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.07,0:08:56.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OO的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.78,0:09:00.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到了  刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.84,0:09:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的聲音  你的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,====================================================
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:21.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲  路易絲！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.53,0:09:25.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.80,0:09:45.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.87,0:09:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年前  我們兩個也像現在這樣看著地球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.70,0:10:01.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候的我  看著這藍色的地球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.00,0:10:04.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定了要在宇宙工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.79,0:10:13.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並想著什麼時候再一次和你一起眺望這景色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.46,0:10:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明都已經決定不再見面了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:27.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我們還是像這樣相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:32.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等你  在這宇宙裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.94,0:10:41.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧  路易絲  回到那時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.39,0:10:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到那無論什麼都很平凡的日常去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.42,0:10:51.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:55.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  你聽到我的聲音了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.29,0:10:56.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.22,0:10:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是被捲進去才會出現在那裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.99,0:11:00.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是指這個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.99,0:11:01.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.77,0:11:10.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將自己奉獻給了統一世界和永久和平的實現
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.66,0:11:15.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了打倒擾亂世界的Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.16,0:11:18.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有為媽媽和爸爸報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:21.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.03,0:11:28.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要妨礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:32.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要阻撓我的話  我會向你開槍…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:36.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪…  很奇怪啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.81,0:11:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前不是這樣的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.10,0:11:42.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼改變了你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.29,0:11:48.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我自己改變了  以我自己的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.65,0:11:49.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是謊話！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:53.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我瞭解你  路易絲 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:56.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你是個溫柔的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.89,0:12:02.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道你為了能去宇宙  非常努力地學習
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.28,0:12:09.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道你想要引起別人注意  笨拙地說些任性的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.71,0:12:16.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道你其實很怕寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:31.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.20,0:12:37.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.10,0:12:41.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.72,0:12:47.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.55,0:12:52.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.93,0:12:56.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.99,0:13:07.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.02,0:13:08.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈萊維準尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.54,0:13:12.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.41,0:13:13.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.43,0:13:13.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.15,0:13:16.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開準尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.12,0:13:23.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用卑劣的手段來迷惑準尉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.29,0:13:45.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這機體  看來果然不擅長近身戰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:47.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的也好不了哪兒去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.91,0:13:49.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只顧著優先強化火力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.93,0:13:52.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不好說  TRANS-AM！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.35,0:14:11.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:19.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:20.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seraphim！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.28,0:14:29.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有話要問你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.41,0:14:32.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖坦白吧  改革者！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.05,0:14:39.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快到TRANS-AM的限制時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.73,0:14:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:44.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會把準尉交給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.77,0:14:50.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡啊  安德烈少尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:53.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這機體…增援嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.14,0:14:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  你為什麼要殺上校！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.09,0:14:59.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩麗絲中尉  你怎麼會活著！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.39,0:15:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.90,0:15:04.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也…背叛了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:09.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有資格說這話嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.39,0:15:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.09,0:15:15.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來一台增援
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.84,0:15:17.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退吧  準尉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.13,0:15:26.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了  瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.90,0:15:27.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別妨礙我！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.26,0:15:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要為上校報仇！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.94,0:15:31.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.48,0:15:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.02,0:15:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都無法改變
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.43,0:15:44.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使報了仇  也不會有人死而復生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.27,0:15:47.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只會徒增悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.77,0:15:53.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是做了這種事  大家就會越來越奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.59,0:16:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能留在原地無法離開  止步不前 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:10.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好一場鬧劇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.77,0:16:12.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那般溫吞的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.61,0:16:17.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在拒絕我這個勁敵嗎  少年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.29,0:16:21.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此  我也有個想法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.82,0:16:36.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這裡就能放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.94,0:16:39.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席琳  我們今後…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:43.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往事前跟克勞德定好的匯合地點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.33,0:16:48.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看情況  你們就在那邊的小屋裡等我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.29,0:16:50.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席琳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.72,0:16:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿不了槍的你跟來也只會拖後腿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.79,0:16:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就照顧好孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.34,0:17:04.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜  我…卡塔隆在戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.86,0:17:26.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:32.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.72,0:17:40.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了奪回路易絲  我會進行我的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:54.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩麗絲中尉在Celestial Being…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.86,0:17:59.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親到底從什麼時候起就背叛軍隊了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.46,0:18:07.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈…沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.22,0:18:13.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準尉  你無法斬斷思念嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.01,0:18:19.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就由我來完成吧  你的期望  你的心願
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.54,0:18:27.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS被擊落一半以上  李拜巴爾上尉被敵人俘虜？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.90,0:18:31.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳聞擁有特許的人  也名不副實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.82,0:18:34.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還不明白啊  我們的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.02,0:18:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是就落得這副德行？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:41.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一次作戰  就只由我們出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.31,0:18:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  誇下海口了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就讓我期待你們的戰果吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:49.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.56,0:18:57.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來晚了  這傢伙就是改革者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.79,0:18:59.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  無庸置疑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.26,0:19:01.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能請你摘下頭盔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.88,0:19:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸會  Celestial Being的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.27,0:19:18.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫李維夫·李拜巴爾  是改革者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.67,0:19:21.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能請你談談關於改革者的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.67,0:19:24.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞琉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.67,0:19:31.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？亞琉  航向偏離預定方向了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.43,0:19:33.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修正一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.39,0:19:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞琉！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:40.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利塔娜小姐！ 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.34,0:19:42.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.33,0:19:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.78,0:19:47.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還用問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.44,0:19:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為  我可是改革者
