Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.49,0:22:09.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本艦的操舵…失靈了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.22,0:22:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況有異常
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.86,0:22:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.97,0:22:15.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還不清楚  但系統全都被刪除
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.31,0:22:17.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.72,0:22:20.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道  是吠陀的介入？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.83,0:22:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你淘氣過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.15,0:22:31.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再擅自行事的話  你心裡有數吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.72,0:22:36.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全無法控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.52,0:22:38.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫離吧  做好小型艇的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.97,0:22:41.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  本艦的所有系統都沒有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.26,0:22:44.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.55,0:22:45.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜·崔尼蒂？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.64,0:22:48.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽我說  這艘艦的系統失靈了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.65,0:22:49.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫幫我們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.20,0:22:54.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  這種事我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.47,0:22:56.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為就是我做的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.65,0:22:57.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.09,0:22:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屏幕…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.95,0:23:01.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.87,0:23:08.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手裡什麼都有  卻還想要更多
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.48,0:23:12.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且內在還空空如也
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.18,0:23:14.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.75,0:23:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都討厭這樣的你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.60,0:23:23.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.20,0:23:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.99,0:23:36.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我要給世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.38,0:23:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留美！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.28,0:23:40.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…帶來變革…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.84,0:23:47.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽！真受不了！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.44,0:24:04.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為改革者而覺醒的亞琉  企圖搶奪OO
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.47,0:24:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fsp40}　{\fsp1}A New Return{\r}\N下集  「亞琉·利塔娜」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.43,0:24:12.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該回到故鄉  還是回到所愛的男人的身邊


